data.description: Enjoy this beautiful 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1 car garage villa located in The Villages of Longwood. Tiles throughout the house with open and functional layout. Kitchen appliances are stainless steel. The owner's suite is spacious and has a large walk-in closet . Large, screened patio that is fenced for privacy, Screens were done in 2022.  A/C= 2022, Roof = 2022, Gutters = 2022. The community amenities include two pools, a clubhouse, sidewalks and street lights. Centrally located less than 5 miles to I95 and 2 miles to downtown.
